text: The moustached brushfinch (Atlapetes albofrenatus) is a species of bird in the family Passerellidae. It is found in northern Colombia, where its natural habitats are subtropical or tropical moist montane forest and heavily degraded former forest. ==References== moustached brush finch Category:Birds of the Colombian Andes Category:Endemic birds of Colombia moustached brush finch
title: Moustached brushfinch
